Key Match Events: Donovan Mitchell sank a jumper with only three-tenths of a second remaining to seal the win for the Cavaliers
Post-Match Reflections: Head coach Doc Rivers made a notable change to the rotation, giving rookie Andre Jackson Jr. extended minutes over Pat Connaughton
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Bucks shot 46% from beyond the arc, their hot start from deep helped them build an early 16-point lead
Others: The Bucks have talent, but with the supporting cast's ongoing struggles, they'll need more time to develop a consistent rhythm
